span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531587\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531587\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 16, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rgt1665702779523.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rgt1665702779523.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rgt1665702779523.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rgt1665702779523\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                       \n Configuring the TXT Connector \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">To configure the TXT connector and data access, edit the application assignment file.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section context\" id=\"rgt1665702779523__context_w3912ab1b5b1_w3913ab1b5_w3914ab1\">\n<div class=\"div context\" id=\"rgt1665702779523__topic_d61409e1_d61410e1_d61411e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rgt1665702779523__p_d61412e1_d61413e1_d61414e1\">The TXT connector is only available on Windows, Linux, and Unix.</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"rgt1665702779523__li_d27017e1_d27018e1_d27019e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">In the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section, specify the connector and version.\n </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[DRIVER_SETTINGS]\nTXT = U2.0</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"rgt1665702779523__li_d27020e1_d27021e1_d27022e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"rgt1665702779523__p_d61415e1_d61416e1_d61417e1\">Optionally, define the default Unicode encoding for all entities handled by the TXT connector. Set the <code class=\"ph codeph\">uni=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">UnicodeEncoding</var> connector option with <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$TXT_PARAMS</span>.\n For example:</span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[DRIVER_SETTINGS]\nTXT = U2.0\nUSYS$TXT_PARAMS uni=utf8</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rgt1665702779523__p_d61418e1_d61419e1_d61420e1\">If this is not present, the default character encoding is used, as defined by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$DEF_CHARSET</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rgt1665702779523__p_d61421e1_d61422e1_d61423e1\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zcj1665702779599.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zcj1665702779599.html\" title=\"Connector option that defines the default Unicode encoding used by the TXT connector. The encoding for a specific entity can be specified using the /uni switch in an entity-to-connector assignment.\">uni</a> and <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fmh1665702657664.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fmh1665702657664.html\" title=\"Set or return the value of $DEF_CHARSET, which defines the character set used for storing data in String fields with C packing code.\">$def_charset</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"rgt1665702779523__li_d27023e1_d27024e1_d27025e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"rgt1665702779523__p_d61424e1_d61425e1_d61426e1\">In the [PATHS] section of the assignment file, define a path for the connector:\n You can then use this definition in path redirections.</span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[PATHS]\n$TXT TXT</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"rgt1665702779523__li_d27026e1_d27027e1_d27028e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"rgt1665702779523__p_d61427e1_d61428e1_d61429e1\">In the [ENTITIES] section. specify the\n               entity-to-path assignments for each entity that reads or writes text files, using the\n               following format: </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>.<var class=\"keyword varname\">Model</var> =\n                        $txt:{<var class=\"keyword varname\">Directory</var>/}<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>.ffd</code>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">/append</code>}\n                        {<code class=\"ph codeph\">/uni=<var class=\"keyword varname\">UnicodeEncoding</var>\n</code>}</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rgt1665702779523__li_d27029e1_d27030e1_d27031e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">/append</code>—enables the TXT\n                     connector to read data from a text file. If omitted, the TXT connector\n                     implicitly creates the file or overwrites it. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rgt1665702779523__li_d27032e1_d27033e1_d27034e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">/uni</code>—specifies the Unicode\n                     encoding to use for a specific entity. If omitted, the encoding defaults to\n                     that specified by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$TXT_PARAMS</span>. </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rgt1665702779523__p_d61430e1_d61431e1_d61432e1\">For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[ENTITIES]\nEntity1.cs $TXT:entity1.fdd/append/uni=utf16\nEntity2.cs $TXT:entity2.fdd/append/uni=utf32</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li></ol></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hjf1719652343883.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Entity-to-Path Assignments</a><p>Entity-to-path assignments are used to provide an additional or alternative name or path for entities.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531587\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531587\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Configuring the TXT Connector Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 16, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Configuring the TXT Connector To configure the TXT connector and data access, edit the application assignment file. The TXT connector is only available on Windows, Linux, and Unix. In the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section, specify the connector and version. [DRIVER_SETTINGS] TXT = U2.0 Copy Optionally, define the default Unicode encoding for all entities handled by the TXT connector. Set the uni= UnicodeEncoding connector option with USYS$TXT_PARAMS . For example: [DRIVER_SETTINGS] TXT = U2.0 USYS$TXT_PARAMS uni=utf8 Copy If this is not present, the default character encoding is used, as defined by $DEF_CHARSET For more information, see uni and $def_charset . In the [PATHS] section of the assignment file, define a path for the connector: You can then use this definition in path redirections. [PATHS] $TXT TXT Copy In the [ENTITIES] section. specify the entity-to-path assignments for each entity that reads or writes text files, using the following format: Entity . Model = $txt:{ Directory /} Entity .ffd { /append } { /uni= UnicodeEncoding } /append —enables the TXT connector to read data from a text file. If omitted, the TXT connector implicitly creates the file or overwrites it. /uni —specifies the Unicode encoding to use for a specific entity. If omitted, the encoding defaults to that specified by USYS$TXT_PARAMS . For example: [ENTITIES] Entity1.cs $TXT:entity1.fdd/append/uni=utf16 Entity2.cs $TXT:entity2.fdd/append/uni=utf32 Copy Related Links Entity-to-Path Assignments Entity-to-path assignments are used to provide an additional or alternative name or path for entities. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}